node.text:
Chocolate Sheet Cakes has always been a popular cake to bring to any gathering, at least in Scandinavia. It is often cut up in small pieces enough for everyone and is loved by kids and adults.

This chocolate sheet cake is fluffy and moist and stays like that for days. It is covered with my " Perfectly Whipped - Salted Caramel Ganache" Unlike most chocolate ganache which stiffens quickly once it´s whipped, this Salted Caramel Ganache variation has a soft and spreadable consistency. It´s perfect for covering this chocolate sheet cake with and so yummy in taste.

The topping is so good I can just eat it by the spoonful on its own. This is such a great combination, and perfect for fall baking, and so delicious, I literally couldn't stop eating this chocolate cake.

The chocolate sheet cake tastes amazing days after, It is so moist and tender and just tastes better and better for each day, As long as you keep it covered at room temp.

#chocolatesheetcake #chocolate #saltedcaramel #ganache #frosting #yummy #sweettooth #eeeeeats #thefeedfeedchocolate #love #canon #sjojoladekake #langpannekake #norge

node.text:
This Raspberry Marshmallow Meringue is truly something special.

It is not too sweet, it is super fluffy, It has an intense raspberry flavor, a beautiful natural pink color. It is super stable and pipes like a dream and tastes so fresh and delicious.

The Raspberry Marshmallow Meringue pairs well wonderfully with a soft and fluffy vanilla cupcake.

node.text:
A Moist gluten-free Carrot Cake filled and covered with a dreamy Hot Cinnamon Spice Mascarpone Frosting that just melts in your mouth.

This carrot cake is so incredibly moist and tender, the combination of the carrot cake with the hot cinnamon mascarpone frosting, each forkful tastes super soft and dreamy.

For the best carrot cake, it is best to use carrots with their tops and not those in plastic bags; it gives prime moisture for this carrot cake. I also use almonds with skin on, which gives this carrot cake a distinctive appearance and texture and delicious! 

I coat the inside of my baking pan with butter and cinnamon sugar which makes for an easy release for these cake layers, and it also tastes delicious!

For the frosting, I steep hot cinnamon tea sachets in warm cream. The lovely flavor of the hot cinnamon tea that is so delicious makes for the best cinnamon frosting and pairs wonderfully with this carrot cake. You're going to love it!

#cinnamon #carrotcake #glutenfree #glutenfreefood #glutenfreerecipes #baking #cake #yummy #sweettooth #canon #macrophotography #video #mascarponecream

node.text:
This banana Meringue Frosting is unique and flavorful in taste; there's something fun about whipping up a meringue frosting with a nostalgic flavor like a banana.

This banana meringue frosting is made with a natural banana flavor; the natural banana flavor is made by steeping very ripe banana slices into boiled water overnight to make banana-infused water.

 The banana-infused water gives an intense banana flavor to your whipped meringue, making this banana meringue frosting so unique and natural in taste, almost like eating a fresh banana.
#banana #frosting #marshmallow #meringue #pipingtechniques #love #yummy #sweettooth #eeats #canon #cupcake #cupcakestagram 

The banana-infused water in the meringue frosting also helps thin out the egg white protein, creating a frosting that melts in your mouth.

Make sure to use a very ripe banana. The dark brown and spotty bananas are the best. The riper the banana is, the more prominent banana flavor you´ll get in your banana meringue frosting.

This batch will modestly frost two layers of 20 cm ( 8inches)  cake, but if you like a loftier frosted look with lots of fluffy swirls. Make 1 1/2 batches.

If you´re a banana fan, you must give this a try.

node.text:
Gluten-free Brookie Pie
This Brookie Pie is made with a chewy, gooey almond cookie layer and baked with a fudgy brownie layer on top.

The almond cookie layer is made from whole almond ( salted or unsalted ). The cookie layer is chewy and gooey and is one of my all-time favorite Norwegian cookie dough recipes, know as kranskekake, normally baked into cookie rings. For the almond cookie dough layer, I prefer using almonds with the skin on them. It tastes so much better and gives a nice texture to the cookie crust.

The fudge brownie layer is made with both unsweetened cocoa powder and dark chocolate and has a fudgy interior and a shiny, glossy crackle top after it is baked. It is a perfect combination together with the chewy almond cookie layer. 

This Brookie Pie is quite rich; I like to chop it into bite-sized pieces, place it in a zip lock bag, place it in the freezer, and save it for a special occasion or enjoy a small piece with my coffee.

I hope you like it as much as I do.
Have a great Sunday

#glutenfree #glutenfritt #brookie #brookiepie #almonds #brownie #fudge #baking #recipe #yummy #sweettooth #eeeeeats #thefeedfeed #thefeedfeedbaking #sunday #kransekake #sjokolade #canon #macrophotography

node.text:
Raspberry & White Vanilla Bean Cake, This white cake is what vanilla dreams are made of.

The white cake layers are soft and tender. It´s made with a vanilla-bean infused cream, The vanilla bean-infused cream turns this delightful cake into something extra-special.

After the cake layers are cooled, I fill the cake layers with homemade marshmallow fluff, kind of like a twinkie cake, which is an iconic American snack cake.

I kind of like the naked style look on this cake as seen in the photo but if you like it sweeter add more marshmallow fluff on top of the cake.

The fresh raspberries make this cake taste so fresh and balance the sweetness of the frosting and make this cake truly crave-worthy.

There is a breath of vanilla in every bite, I hope you fall in love with this white vanilla bean cake. 

#cake #twinkiecake #raspberry #summer #whitevanillacake #marshmallows #summervibes #decoration #recipes #cakerecipes #frosting #yummy #sweettooth #eeats #thefeedfeed #canon #macrophotography

node.text:
This Mocca Meringues Ice Cream cake is beyond delicious.

The cake layer is a gooey chocolate almond meringue cake.
After it is baked it is topped with a delicious Mocca ice cream, that is combined with crushed Mocca meringues.

The cake crust is gluten-free so anyone can enjoy it.
The combination of the gooey chocolate almond meringue cake, and the Mocca ice cream, combined with the crushed Mocca meringues is just something you need to make and taste to understand how delicious this ice cream cake is.

It´s the perfect ice cream cake to make in advance as it keeps well for up to two weeks in the freezer and such a crowd-pleaser. 

#glutenfree #icecream #icecreamcake #mocca #coffee #meringue #baking #recipe #favorite #macrophotography

node.text:
Using Greek Yogurt in whipped Cream makes it thick, extra creamy, and more stable than just whipped cream.

Greek Yogurt adds a subtle tanginess to the whipped cream that pairs beautifully with fresh passion fruit.

This frosting is so incredibly delicious, it´s light, creamy, thick, and the perfect summertime flavors.

You want to eat this by the spoonful it is so good!

This frosting can be used as a topping on a pavlova, as a filling inside or on the outside of your cake, or pipe onto a cupcake, or serve on the side with some strawberries or other berries.

This frosting is perfect for summer, I hope you love it as much as I do.

With Love
